attributes.description: Mayur Uniquoters is primarily engaged in the business of manufacturing of Coated Textile Fabrics, artificial leather and PVC Vinyl which are widely used in different segments such as Footwear, Furnishings, Automotive OEM, Automotive replacement market, and Automotive Exports.
